]]></沿革內容>
<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standard is prescribed in accordance with the provisions of Article 17 of the Act Governing Food Sanitation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This standard applies to bottled and packaged drinking water which is suitable for consumption.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The quality of the source water used in the production of packaged drinking water shall meet the requirement of「Quality Standard of Source Water for Drinking Water」.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Maximum tolerance of heavy metals:
┌──────┬───────────┐
│Heavy metal │Maximum tolerance     │
├──────┼───────────┤
│As          │0.01 ppm              │
├──────┼───────────┤    
│Pb          │0.05 ppm              │
├──────┼───────────┤
│Zn          │ 5.0 ppm              │
├──────┼───────────┤
│Cu          │ 1.0 ppm              │
├──────┼───────────┤
│Hg          │0.001 ppm             │
├──────┼───────────┤
│Cd          │0.005 ppm             │
└──────┴───────────┘
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Microbiological criteria (Only applied to bottled and packaged drinking water which is suitable for direct consumption):
┌────────────┬──────────┐
│Microorganism           │Limit               │
├────────────┼──────────┤
│Coliform bacteria       │Negative            │
├────────────┼──────────┤
│Fecal Streptococci      │Negative            │
├────────────┼──────────┤
│Pseudomonas aeruginosa  │Negative            │
└────────────┴──────────┘
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 6</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Maximum tolerance of bromate: 0.01ppm.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 7</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standard shall be implemented from the date of promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
